dct_title_s: Palestine ancienne & moderne d'après les sources les plus authentiques
dct_description_sm: Covers portions of Israel, Jordan, Syria and Lebanon. Relief shown by hachures. Depth shown by sounding and isolines. Insets: [Sinai] (Scale [ca. 1:2,600,000]) -- Golfe de Suez -- [Cross section of the Palestine from the source of the Jordan to the Red Sea] -- [Panoramic view of the mountains of Palestine] -- Jérusalem d'après le plan de G. Williams (Scale [ca. 1:80,000]). "No. 18." "Atlas usuel No. 23." "Atlas universel No.36." Includes notes and index.
